Class DataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.md2k.mcerebrum.api.core.datakitapi.AbstractDataSource
      • org.md2k.mcerebrum.api.core.datakitapi.DataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataSourceCreator, DataSourceReadWrite

    public abstract class DataSource
extends AbstractDataSource
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Base class for DataSourceReadWrite and DataSourceCreator. This class exposes the protected getter methods from AbstractDataSource.
